      "translations": {
        "zh": "关关雎鸠，在河之洲。\n窈窕淑女，君子好逑。\n——佚名《关雎》",
        "en": "By riverside a pair\nOf turtledoves are cooing;\nThere is a maiden fair\nWhom a young man is wooing.\n--Cooing and Wooing"
